â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ notification-service/     # ğŸ” Opsional: notifikasi stok / laporan
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ file-storage-service/     # ğŸ” Opsional: upload logo, gambar produk
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ audit-service/            # ğŸ” Opsional: jejak audit
